title: Sony GTK XB90 High Power Home Audio System
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the GTK XB90 sound system from Sony.  This speaker is ideal for someone looking for big bass that can be used without needing to be plugged into a power outlet.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com or call us at 800-860-3736.
